<div id="tab9">
<h1>Mediums</h1>
<b>Spirit Stone</b><br>
A blue stone about the size of an American Quarter and shaped like a teardrop, hangs around her neck on a silver chain. This Spirit Stone can channel and hold Faith Magic and increases the effects of the magic, acting as a boost and allowing each Faith Spell to be more powerful than usual. If X lifts the stone to her mouth and speaks through it to specific spirits, it allows her to contact them faster. (Reduces summoning spirits to one post per spirit.)
</div>

